Name: The Guild Garage
Title: Precious Metal
Desc: At the Pomona Swap Meet and Classic Car Show, David falls in love with a 1954 Fiat 500 Topolino.
LongDescription: While attending the Pomona Swap Meet and Classic Car Show, David falls in love with a 1954 Fiat 500 Topolino, but the Lowriders are what really get his attention; they head to San Diego where David gets to ride in a 1966 Lamborghini 400 GT.
